  You may request custom subsets of the data in the following formats:

     * Plotted image (GIF)
     * Spreadsheet
     * NetCDF file
     * Tab-delimited file
     * Comma-delimited file
     * Generic ASCII file

  Subsets may be chosen on various space-time axes:

     * Longitude-Latitude plane
     * Monthly time series
     * Profiles along lines of longitude or latitude
     * Longitude or latitude profiles vs time

